There's nothing to be afraid of, nothing is happening.
安静，听我说 不怕，没事的

23
00:02:42,920000 --> 00:02:45,160000
Nothing is happening.
没事的

24
00:02:45,160000 --> 00:02:50,234000
- Hi, hi. - Hi, hi.
没事的

25
00:02:54,400000 --> 00:02:57,119000
Hi.
没事的

26
00:02:59,720000 --> 00:03:04,991000
- Excuse me - Henrik, easy does it.
抱歉 汉瑞，放轻松

27
