You must keep him under control.
你必须照料他，别让他乱来

28
00:03:09,993000 --> 00:03:15,000000
- He won't do anything. - I must consider the other diners.
他不会乱来的 但我得为其他客人着想

29
00:03:15,000000 --> 00:03:20,000000
Henrik, Henrik, where are you going?
是…汉瑞，你去哪儿？ 克罗斯快来了

30
00:03:20,000000 --> 00:03:22,440000
- Where are you going? - Klaus is coming.
克罗斯快来了，过来

31
00:03:22,440000 --> 00:03:24,910000
Let's sit down again like the waiter wants.
服务生要我们坐下来

32
00:03:24,910000 --> 00:03:27,080000
Shut up!
闭嘴！

33
00:03:27,080000 --> 00:03:27,080000
